---
import en from '../i18n/locales/en.json';
import es from '../i18n/locales/es.json';

const lang = Astro.props.lang || 'en';
const translations = lang === 'es' ? es : en;
const t = (key) => translations[key] || key;
---

<section class="faq">
	<div class="section-header">
		<h2>{t('faq.title')}</h2>
		<p class="section-subtitle">{t('faq.subtitle')}</p>
	</div>

	<div class="faq-container">
		<details class="faq-item">
			<summary class="faq-question">{t('faq.q1')}</summary>
			<div class="faq-answer">
				<p>Your website could be losing customers if it's slow, doesn't rank in local search, or doesn't convert visitors into leads. We offer a free performance audit that identifies exactly what's holding your site back and what improvements could generate revenue immediately.</p>
			</div>
		</details>

		<details class="faq-item">
			<summary class="faq-question">{t('faq.q2')}</summary>
			<div class="faq-answer">
				<p>Over 50% of mobile searches have local intent. Customers actively search for businesses like yours on Google Maps and local search results. If you're not ranking there, you're losing customers to competitors who are. Local SEO builds visibility exactly where your customers are searching.</p>
			</div>
		</details>

		<details class="faq-item">
			<summary class="faq-question">{t('faq.q3')}</summary>
			<div class="faq-answer">
				<p>It depends on your current position and the competition. Typically, initial ranking improvements appear within 30-60 days. Major ranking shifts and significant traffic growth usually take 3-6 months of consistent optimization. We focus on sustainable growth, not quick fixes.</p>
			</div>
		</details>

		<details class="faq-item">
			<summary class="faq-question">{t('faq.q4')}</summary>
			<div class="faq-answer">
				<p>Our free performance audit includes: page speed analysis, Google Maps visibility check, website conversion analysis, local SEO competitor comparison, technical SEO issues, mobile usability assessment, online reputation analysis, and actionable recommendations you can implement immediately. You'll get a clear roadmap for growth without any obligation.</p>
			</div>
		</details>

		<details class="faq-item">
			<summary class="faq-question">{t('faq.q5')}</summary>
			<div class="faq-answer">
				<p>Automation systems handle repetitive tasks automatically—lead capture, follow-up sequences, CRM data entry, appointment scheduling, and customer segmentation. This frees you to focus on growth while processes run. We implement CRM systems and workflows that scale your business without scaling your team proportionally.</p>
			</div>
		</details>

		<details class="faq-item">
			<summary class="faq-question">{t('faq.q6')}</summary>
			<div class="faq-answer">
				<p>We start with a free 30-minute discovery call where we listen to your goals, current challenges, and what success looks like for you. We'll explain our process, answer your questions, and determine if we're the right fit. No pressure, just clarity about how we can help you grow.</p>
			</div>
		</details>
	</div>
</section>


